OL,3,CMan dies after accidentally running in
OL,4,Cfront of train
OL,6,FA man who accidentally ran in front of
OL,7,Fa train was listening to music too
OL,8,Floud at the time of his death, an
OL,9,Finquest heard.
OL,11,FSam Dudley, 29, had been wearing
OL,12,Fheadphones on a run when he was hit at
OL,13,Fa level crossing in Formby, known
OL,14,Flocally as Hoggs Hill level crossing.
