OL,3,CMan dies after accidentally running in
OL,4,Cfront of train
OL,6,FBefore getting to the tracks, there is
OL,7,Fsignage and a traffic light which
OL,8,Fshows red or green depending on
OL,9,Fwhether a train is approaching. When a
OL,10,Ftrain approaches the crossing, the
OL,11,Flight flashes red and a siren will
OL,12,Fsound.
OL,14,FAs Sam ran onto the tracks, the light
OL,15,Fhad flashed and the klaxon had
OL,16,Fsounded, with CCTV showing Sam run
OL,17,Fonto the track before appearing
OL,18,Fimmediately shocked when he sees the
OL,19,Ftrain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
