OL,3,CMan dies after accidentally running in
OL,4,Cfront of train
OL,6,FAn investigation revealed Sam had
OL,7,Fentered the track through the level
OL,8,Fcrossing using the pedestrian gate
OL,9,Fwhile the red light and klaxon were
OL,10,Fon. After the gate there is further
OL,11,Fthere is signage warning of oncoming
OL,12,Ftrains.
OL,14,FSenior coroner Anita Bhardwaj states
OL,15,Fin the report the "crossing was safe
OL,16,Fand compliant" and there "were no
OL,17,Fcausal or contributory failings
OL,18,Fidentified in the inspection,
OL,19,Fmaintenance, or management of the
OL,20,Fcrossing".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
