OL,3,CMan dies after accidentally running in
OL,4,Cfront of train
OL,6,FMs Bhardwaj said: "It is more likely
OL,7,Fthan not that Sam did not hear the
OL,8,Fklaxon because he was running whilst
OL,9,Flistening to loud music through his
OL,10,Fheadphones.
OL,12,F"In all the circumstances it is more
OL,13,Flikely than not Sam was distracted,
OL,14,Fnot fully attentive and proceeded onto
OL,15,Fthe track."
OL,17,FDespite this, the senior coroner for
OL,18,FSefton, St Helens and Knowsley, found
OL,19,Fmatters of concern following her
OL,20,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
