OL,6,F"Visual cues generally attract initial
OL,7,Fattention more effectively and support
OL,8,Frapid comprehension, while sound cues
OL,9,Ftend to create a stronger emotional
OL,10,Fconnection.
OL,12,F"However, using both visual and
OL,13,Fauditory cues may together provide a
OL,14,Fmore effective form of communication."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
